{"tid":1968599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國之音發聲明 反駁白宮「中國宣傳機器」指控","createTime":"2020-04-11T18:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T21:32:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8a1539b1c737f53a7df331436c02316e4c5dc3","tid":1968599,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/X1DMMGQTIUdycWdo1WfWBPk6tn4=/1024x576/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/V57CS72VG6IEBZTFFFYL53JTVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FX1DMMGQTIUdycWdo1WfWBPk6tn4%3D%2F1024x576%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FV57CS72VG6IEBZTFFFYL53JTVM.jpg&h=64f91b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國早前批評美國之音收取納稅人稅金，卻淪為中國喉舌。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音台長貝內特（Amanda Bennett）周五（11日）發聲明反駁指控，不點名特朗普政府指，美國之音在很早以前已經報道中國隱瞞武漢肺炎疫情的新聞，揭穿北京和官方控制傳媒的手段。<br />\n<br />\n總部位於美國紐約的保護記者委員會（Committee to Protect Journalists，CPJ）也譴責白宮的說法過份，並破壞美國之音在世界各地的工作。<br />\n美國白宮早前指，美國之音每年獲2億美元（約15.5億港元）資助，應當報道事實、講美國故事、及清楚有效地表達美國政策，但美國之音卻擴大北京的宣傳；白宮批評，美國之音在twitter播放中國慶祝武漢解封的影片中，引用中國官方數據，並指稱美國的武漢肺炎人數已經超越中國，是在為北京宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n中方早前驅逐3間美媒駐華記者，包括《華爾街日報》、《華盛頓郵報》和《紐約時報》；另要求美國之音及《時代周刊》向中國政府提交營運資料。<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200411/5MABDERJRLUJ5WVIPXJYDTFB4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200411%2F5MABDERJRLUJ5WVIPXJYDTFB4Q%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W2%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=5eeb3595\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200411%2F5MABDERJRLUJ5WVIPXJYDTFB4Q%2F&h=15b59f2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200411/5MABDERJRLUJ5WVIPXJYDTFB4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"6caa70bbbd66c1484b45e5ec0d16f1e66e2e1a79","tid":1968599,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:18:36.000Z","msg":"特朗普搵fbi查下D人好過嘴炮啦"},{"pid":"56de1b82fbf69c48396c6b31e35a5f8bf6955d88","tid":1968599,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:33:42.000Z","msg":"港台收政府錢鬧政府 點解無人幫政府講說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明一樣情況"},{"pid":"769957bb372bb9131e3fc754a758634c9563a829","tid":1968599,"uid":296369,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:46:31.000Z","msg":"VOA 真係親咗中，睇吓佢哋d新聞已經冇以前咁客觀，佢哋有約章，應該以報導美國為主，要客觀中肯.......但走咗去報支那，VOA 不在美國境內報導只在境外，但又唔係政府舌喉，可能Trump 想郁Amanda, 機構內已經有被滲透....."},{"pid":"5d83b52b5285796523b4238c283d2a2a9dd814ae","tid":1968599,"uid":123970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:49:01.000Z","msg":"早兩年郭文貴直播中斷單野, 唔係以為炒幾個small potato就過到骨下話? 高層班共碟美奸博人唔記得扮無辜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7f3fe1f1e204d94fc7c0409698889fc2c04ff2","tid":1968599,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T19:56:33.000Z","msg":"報導武漢肺炎唔代表唔親中<br />\n正如白粉報都屌過政府屌過黑警"},{"pid":"1cfb4ebb4fdca1766bc3b0de41f9f594cf61b09e","tid":1968599,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T21:32:30.000Z","msg":"VoA個角色好唔同，有一半係宣傳機器嚟，再係咁內鬥，遲下會咬死埋自己班左翼媒體"}]}